    "detail": "We have been staying 3 nights at the Yamagata Kaku Hotel & Spa. Steven and the hotel staff have made our stay magnificent. It is brand new hotel with all commodities, fitness center, spa and restaurants. Guess rooms are spacious and each bathroom has large hot springs bath. Seldom we have been welcomed as we have been in this hotel. Mark has kindly organised a whole day hiking trip for us to visit the best of spots/hiking trails/waterfalls in Jiaoxi/Yilan. I would deeply recommend the Yamagata hotel for the dedication and kindest of the staff made towards the guests. I wish all the deemed success to the Yamagata Kaku hôtel & spa",
